org.red5.server.stream.consumer

Class ImmutableTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.red5.server.stream.consumer.ImmutableTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.red5.io.IoConstants, org.red5.io.ITag

    public class ImmutableTag
extends Object
implements org.red5.io.ITag
    An ImmutableTag represents immutable encapsulation of flash media data. The timestamp is the only mutable field.
    Author:
    Paul Gregoire (mondain@gmail.com)
